This is the FieldTrip REALTIME module. It contains MATLAB functions and
compiled executables to interface various EEG, MEG, MRI and NIRS acquisition
systems to MATLAB using the FieldTrip buffer as the interface.

For more information please visit http://www.fieldtriptoolbox.org/development/realtime

